models :

1 - User Model :

	* username
	* password
	* user_type ( administrators , employees , external_accountants , anonymous_users )
	* email 
	* branch_id ( R&D , Sales , Manufacturing ) for employees only - one to many relation
	* active


a ) only admins can create a new account ( no signup )
b ) only admins can create and modify a user



2 - Branch Model :

	* branch_name
	* branch_description

a ) admins only should assign branches for employees only
b ) admins only should add and remove company branches


4 - Item Model :
	
	* name
	* description
	* branch ( many to many relationship )
	* photo
	* price
	* total_count
	* tags   ( many to many relationship )



a ) only admins and employees can add or edit items
b ) if employee and item in the same branch , employee can add or modify 


5 - Tag Model :

	* name
	* description

== Special Pages ::

* summarize current status of the inventory
* grouping items by branches and tags
* total items in a given branch
* external accountants can view only ( items and summary pages only )
== Authentication ::

* authentication using Username/Password
* anonymous can only access login screen

=========================================================================================================================================================================================

@@ SYSTEM PAGES @@

1 - Authentication Pages :

	a ) login
	b ) logout

2 - User CRUD [create|read|update|delete] ( Admin only )
3 - Branch CRUD [create|read|update|delete] ( Admin only )
4 - Item CRUD [create|read|update|delete] ( Admin , Employee if only employee.branch == item.branch , accountant only [all|show] )
5 - Tag CRUD [create|read|update|delete]  ( Admin and Employee )
6 - Summary Page [ All Branches Div , All Tags Div , Items Data Div ] 




